1
00:00:40,479 --> 00:00:42,960
The capillaries on your chest are constantly expanding,

2
00:00:43,399 --> 00:00:45,159
which has severely affected

3
00:00:45,159 --> 00:00:46,479
the blood supply function of your heart.

4
00:00:48,200 --> 00:00:49,439
How much longer do I have?

5
00:00:49,560 --> 00:00:50,359
Three months

6
00:00:50,719 --> 00:00:52,200
is the most optimistic estimate.

7
00:00:53,880 --> 00:00:55,399
It doesn't matter who I am.

8
00:00:55,880 --> 00:01:00,359
But I also have an eyeball scar on my back.

9
00:01:00,759 --> 00:01:03,759
To cure it, you can only save yourself.

10
00:01:03,840 --> 00:01:06,519
If you don't go in person this time,

11
00:01:06,680 --> 00:01:07,640
do you think

12
00:01:08,079 --> 00:01:10,079
those friends of yours

13
00:01:10,519 --> 00:01:12,359
will be able to survive?

14
00:01:28,319 --> 00:01:29,319
Fatty!

15
00:01:29,840 --> 00:01:31,920
That giant spider is coming for me!

16
00:01:33,280 --> 00:01:33,920
What are you doing?

17
00:01:44,239 --> 00:01:47,560
This is the true main hall of Princess Xian'an.

18
00:01:49,680 --> 00:01:50,719
Isn't it beautiful?

19
00:01:59,599 --> 00:02:01,319
The chance to witness the true power of the Lingxiao Pearl

20
00:02:01,319 --> 00:02:02,359
is right before our eyes.

21
00:02:02,359 --> 00:02:04,560
If this Lingxiao Pearl can resurrect the princess,

22
00:02:04,680 --> 00:02:06,640
then it can definitely save Chen Youxi's life.

23
00:02:10,960 --> 00:02:11,560
Shutong!

24
00:02:56,360 --> 00:02:57,960
Old Chen, how's your research going?

25
00:02:57,960 --> 00:02:59,000
You should look into it.

26
00:02:59,000 --> 00:03:00,919
Staff Officer He, give us some advice.

27
00:03:06,960 --> 00:03:08,039
What's the big deal?

28
00:03:08,039 --> 00:03:09,240
Chatting sneakily over here

29
00:03:09,240 --> 00:03:10,319
without including me.

30
00:03:10,719 --> 00:03:12,439
Aren't we a team?

31
00:03:12,919 --> 00:03:14,319
Wh- What is this thing?

32
00:03:15,599 --> 00:03:17,240
The chart Bai Lingling used for the sacrifice.

33
00:03:22,800 --> 00:03:24,759
How did this thing end up in your hands?

34
00:03:25,639 --> 00:03:26,319
Take a guess.

35
00:03:27,719 --> 00:03:28,439
Sister,

36
00:03:29,000 --> 00:03:29,879
when we get back,

37
00:03:30,199 --> 00:03:31,719
come to our little shop for some tea.

38
00:03:31,919 --> 00:03:32,599
Really.

39
00:03:32,719 --> 00:03:35,319
This is my business card.

40
00:03:35,639 --> 00:03:37,280
All right, it's enough that you know him.

41
00:03:37,319 --> 00:03:38,479
You can find us anywhere.

42
00:03:38,479 --> 00:03:39,319
You can find us.

43
00:03:40,919 --> 00:03:41,759
As for this,

44
00:03:42,000 --> 00:03:44,560
I think it's a genealogy.

45
00:03:45,280 --> 00:03:46,120
No kidding.

46
00:03:46,360 --> 00:03:47,639
We could all tell.

47
00:03:47,680 --> 00:03:49,120
When Bai Lingling was performing the sacrifice,

48
00:03:49,120 --> 00:03:51,560
this thing was placed right next to the coffin.

49
00:03:52,159 --> 00:03:52,800
I think

50
00:03:52,800 --> 00:03:53,800
it must have

51
00:03:53,800 --> 00:03:56,000
information related to the Lingxiao Pearl on it.

52
00:03:56,919 --> 00:03:58,439
Do you still think

53
00:03:58,960 --> 00:04:01,800
that this Lingxiao Pearl and Old Chen's curse

54
00:04:01,800 --> 00:04:02,840
are related?

55
00:04:02,840 --> 00:04:04,000
Of course.

56
00:04:04,120 --> 00:04:05,479
Otherwise, why would Bai Lingling's boss

57
00:04:05,680 --> 00:04:06,439
go through so much trouble

58
00:04:06,439 --> 00:04:08,199
just to find the Lingxiao Pearl?

59
00:04:08,439 --> 00:04:08,840
Right.

60
00:04:08,840 --> 00:04:11,159
But this is our only clue right now.

61
00:04:11,439 --> 00:04:13,039
We can only focus our efforts on this.

62
00:04:24,079 --> 00:04:25,160
This wound of yours,

63
00:04:26,199 --> 00:04:27,439
it'll probably leave a scar.

64
00:04:28,079 --> 00:04:30,399
In the palm of my hand, a scar is fine.

65
00:04:32,879 --> 00:04:33,839
According to what you're saying,

66
00:04:34,480 --> 00:04:35,839
there's actually an advantage to it.

67
00:04:36,199 --> 00:04:37,199
What advantage?

68
00:04:39,000 --> 00:04:40,240
It constantly reminds you

69
00:04:40,720 --> 00:04:42,160
not to make dangerous decisions anymore.

70
00:04:43,079 --> 00:04:45,759
But if I encounter the same situation again,

71
00:04:46,439 --> 00:04:49,399
I'd probably still make the same decision.

72
00:04:51,800 --> 00:04:52,360
Haven't you ever thought about

73
00:04:52,360 --> 00:04:54,240
how much blood Bai Lingling actually needs?

74
00:04:55,040 --> 00:04:57,079
How much blood do you have to give her?

75
00:05:02,759 --> 00:05:03,759
There won't be a next time.

76
00:05:05,000 --> 00:05:07,279
I don't want you to face any more danger because of me.

77
00:05:09,040 --> 00:05:11,439
You don't get a say in my business.

78
00:05:13,920 --> 00:05:14,680
Then tell me,

79
00:05:15,120 --> 00:05:16,120
how do I get a say?

80
00:05:19,160 --> 00:05:20,199
Go abroad with me.

81
00:05:28,319 --> 00:05:30,399
This is the structural map of the princess's tomb that I drew.

82
00:05:30,959 --> 00:05:33,079
Those people caused some damage to the tomb.

83
00:05:33,800 --> 00:05:35,639
I hope this map can be of some help.

84
00:05:36,000 --> 00:05:36,839
That's great.

85
00:05:36,839 --> 00:05:38,000
I'll hand it in when the time comes.

86
00:05:38,680 --> 00:05:39,399
By the way.

87
00:05:39,720 --> 00:05:41,199
In about half a month,

88
00:05:41,480 --> 00:05:43,439
we will hold an academic seminar

89
00:05:43,680 --> 00:05:46,000
specifically for this Yunling archaeological research.

90
00:05:46,439 --> 00:05:48,600
Some artifacts will also be exhibited.

91
00:05:48,600 --> 00:05:49,360
Are you coming?

92
00:05:49,360 --> 00:05:50,879
I'll pass on this kind of occasion.

93
00:05:52,680 --> 00:05:53,560
What about Bai Lingling?

94
00:05:53,639 --> 00:05:55,319
Still no news of her from the police?

95
00:05:55,879 --> 00:05:56,560
No.

96
00:05:56,759 --> 00:05:57,800
After you came back this time,

97
00:05:57,800 --> 00:05:59,160
have you been to the hospital for a checkup?

98
00:05:59,160 --> 00:05:59,839
Not yet.

99
00:05:59,839 --> 00:06:01,000
But I suspect

100
00:06:01,000 --> 00:06:02,360
my sudden fainting

101
00:06:02,360 --> 00:06:04,240
might also be related to the Lingxiao Pearl.

102
00:06:05,040 --> 00:06:06,279
You mean the one you mentioned,

103
00:06:06,720 --> 00:06:09,079
the luminous pearl that might contain infinite energy?

104
00:06:09,079 --> 00:06:09,839
Yes, yes, yes.

105
00:06:10,360 --> 00:06:11,399
Bai Lingling and her gang

106
00:06:11,480 --> 00:06:13,399
were also after the Lingxiao Pearl this time.

107
00:06:13,439 --> 00:06:14,720
And according to her,

108
00:06:15,120 --> 00:06:16,160
her boss

109
00:06:16,160 --> 00:06:18,279
has been tracking the whereabouts of the Lingxiao Pearl.

110
00:06:18,399 --> 00:06:19,720
This so-called Lingxiao Pearl,

111
00:06:20,079 --> 00:06:20,879
to us,

112
00:06:20,879 --> 00:06:22,680
has very important archaeological significance.

113
00:06:22,680 --> 00:06:23,399
Exactly.

114
00:06:23,480 --> 00:06:25,759
But the Lingxiao Pearl is not in our hands right now.

115
00:06:26,160 --> 00:06:29,160
If we want to figure out the civilization of this eyeball totem,

116
00:06:29,319 --> 00:06:32,120
we'll probably have to wait for the Yunling archaeological results.

117
00:06:32,759 --> 00:06:33,680
Bai Lingling also said

118
00:06:33,680 --> 00:06:35,519
there is more than one Lingxiao Pearl.

119
00:06:35,959 --> 00:06:37,439
I'll look into it later on my end.

120
00:06:41,040 --> 00:06:41,560
Sound good?

121
00:06:41,560 --> 00:06:42,480
Good, good, good.

122
00:06:43,800 --> 00:06:44,800
What were you thinking?

123
00:06:44,839 --> 00:06:45,560
From now on, we'll just...

124
00:06:46,399 --> 00:06:47,480
Yeah, right?

125
00:06:47,519 --> 00:06:49,759
How could you come up with such a method?

126
00:06:50,360 --> 00:06:51,480
That's great.

127
00:06:52,199 --> 00:06:53,000
Ladies,

128
00:06:53,680 --> 00:06:54,720
this is not cool, is it?

129
00:06:55,199 --> 00:06:57,000
I paid you all

130
00:06:57,120 --> 00:06:58,319
to help me build up the patina.

131
00:06:58,560 --> 00:07:00,399
And you're just standing here laughing and joking. You...

132
00:07:00,399 --> 00:07:01,120
Boss,

133
00:07:01,240 --> 00:07:02,839
this time, we don't need to do the work.

134
00:07:02,879 --> 00:07:04,360
Let us show you something new.

135
00:07:05,519 --> 00:07:06,399
The boss is here.

136
00:07:06,399 --> 00:07:07,560
Look, boss.

137
00:07:07,639 --> 00:07:08,639
Please take a look.

138
00:07:16,360 --> 00:07:17,160
This is interesting.

139
00:07:22,439 --> 00:07:24,000
Isn't this my electric fan?

140
00:07:24,000 --> 00:07:24,759
Yeah.

141
00:07:24,959 --> 00:07:26,160
I figured since it's winter,

142
00:07:26,160 --> 00:07:27,879
it's just sitting there useless anyway.

143
00:07:27,959 --> 00:07:28,959
So I was thinking,

144
00:07:29,160 --> 00:07:30,360
after modifying it like this,

145
00:07:30,600 --> 00:07:32,399
we can use it to do the work from now on.

146
00:07:32,399 --> 00:07:34,759
We can just stand by and watch.

147
00:07:34,800 --> 00:07:35,759
That's great.

148
00:07:38,519 --> 00:07:39,240
Well,

149
00:07:40,199 --> 00:07:41,959
how many days have we worked this month?

150
00:07:41,959 --> 00:07:43,000
Ten days.

151
00:07:43,360 --> 00:07:44,319
Two bucks a day.

152
00:07:44,680 --> 00:07:45,720
Ten days is twenty bucks.

153
00:07:46,120 --> 00:07:47,600
Let me settle the bill for everyone.

154
00:07:48,000 --> 00:07:48,600
Here's yours.

155
00:07:49,279 --> 00:07:50,319
Twenty.

156
00:07:50,879 --> 00:07:51,879
And here's yours.

157
00:07:52,160 --> 00:07:52,959
As a bonus,

158
00:07:52,959 --> 00:07:53,759
Thank you, thank you. Thanks, boss.

159
00:07:53,759 --> 00:07:55,360
I'll take out another twenty bucks.

160
00:07:55,360 --> 00:07:57,199
You four go have a nice meal.

161
00:07:57,319 --> 00:07:58,879
It's my treat, Lao Lu.

162
00:08:00,000 --> 00:08:00,759
That's so nice.

163
00:08:01,000 --> 00:08:01,839
Starting tomorrow,

164
00:08:01,839 --> 00:08:03,040
you ladies don't need to come anymore.

165
00:08:03,759 --> 00:08:04,720
Why?

166
00:08:04,920 --> 00:08:05,879
Now that I have this,

167
00:08:05,920 --> 00:08:08,000
you guys are useless.

168
00:08:08,319 --> 00:08:09,040
Ladies,

169
00:08:09,040 --> 00:08:10,480
I have friends coming over later.

170
00:08:10,480 --> 00:08:11,199
Everyone,

171
00:08:11,439 --> 00:08:12,319
see you around.

172
00:08:12,519 --> 00:08:14,480
You only care about us when you need us.

173
00:08:14,480 --> 00:08:14,959
Let's go.

174
00:08:15,319 --> 00:08:15,879
Let me tell you,

175
00:08:15,879 --> 00:08:17,000
you wasteful woman.

176
00:08:17,000 --> 00:08:18,000
Let's go, let's go.

177
00:08:18,160 --> 00:08:19,319
I'll give you a trophy.

178
00:08:20,199 --> 00:08:21,120
An invention award.

179
00:08:21,439 --> 00:08:23,240
Best Invention Award.

180
00:08:23,600 --> 00:08:24,279
Lao Lu.

181
00:08:25,240 --> 00:08:26,160
What are you playing with?

182
00:08:26,240 --> 00:08:27,639
I heard you laughing from the door.

183
00:08:27,680 --> 00:08:29,480
It's about to take off.

184
00:08:30,199 --> 00:08:31,800
I just fired the four aunties.

185
00:08:31,839 --> 00:08:33,600
With this, I'll save money.

186
00:08:33,600 --> 00:08:34,679
A new invention?

187
00:08:35,559 --> 00:08:36,600
Sit, sit, sit.

188
00:08:40,000 --> 00:08:41,440
I called you two here today

189
00:08:41,480 --> 00:08:43,559
mainly to give you some small gifts.

190
00:08:43,559 --> 00:08:44,879
Just a little token of my appreciation.

191
00:08:45,039 --> 00:08:46,480
It's nothing much.

192
00:08:46,639 --> 00:08:49,200
This is made of our Wenxiang Jade.

193
00:08:49,840 --> 00:08:51,039
It's a whistle.

194
00:08:51,039 --> 00:08:52,240
A survival whistle.

195
00:08:52,799 --> 00:08:54,240
For big Fatty.

196
00:08:55,240 --> 00:08:56,399
Thanks, thanks, thanks.

197
00:08:56,600 --> 00:08:57,200
Lao Chen,

198
00:08:57,200 --> 00:08:58,840
didn't you lose the end of your rope?

199
00:08:59,200 --> 00:09:00,320
I made a metal one for you.

200
00:09:00,320 --> 00:09:02,240
Finely crafted with hidden mechanisms.

201
00:09:02,279 --> 00:09:03,240
Take a look, isn't it beautiful?

202
00:09:03,240 --> 00:09:04,360
That's very thoughtful of you, Lao Lu.

203
00:09:06,039 --> 00:09:06,840
And this.

204
00:09:06,840 --> 00:09:07,799
A pair of earrings.

205
00:09:07,799 --> 00:09:09,559
It has a Taotie pattern on it.

206
00:09:09,679 --> 00:09:11,279
This is for Staff Officer He.

207
00:09:11,279 --> 00:09:12,600
Please pass it on to her for me.

208
00:09:12,600 --> 00:09:13,799
Okay, put it there.

209
00:09:14,200 --> 00:09:15,240
Fatty will take it back.

210
00:09:16,360 --> 00:09:17,679
Why am I involved in this?

211
00:09:22,440 --> 00:09:23,600
Then you can do it for me.

212
00:09:24,440 --> 00:09:25,120
Lao Lu,

213
00:09:25,879 --> 00:09:27,440
how's the research on the genealogy book going?

214
00:09:27,639 --> 00:09:29,039
I'm researching it. Every day.

215
00:09:29,759 --> 00:09:31,080
Just these few pages

216
00:09:31,200 --> 00:09:32,639
are making my brain split open.

217
00:09:32,639 --> 00:09:35,000
If there really is important information on it,

218
00:09:35,159 --> 00:09:37,799
Bai Lingling will definitely try everything to get it back.

219
00:09:38,480 --> 00:09:39,840
Then I'll hide it.

220
00:09:40,480 --> 00:09:41,679
I'll hide it

221
00:09:42,080 --> 00:09:44,639
right under our Buddhist shrine.

222
00:09:45,559 --> 00:09:46,240
Alright.

223
00:09:47,039 --> 00:09:48,600
You guys keep chatting, keep chatting.

224
00:09:55,279 --> 00:09:56,759
What's the matter? She's gone?

225
00:09:56,799 --> 00:09:57,799
Ever since we got back,

226
00:09:58,080 --> 00:09:59,440
Staff Officer He has been staying at the hotel.

227
00:09:59,440 --> 00:10:00,480
She's been there for over half a month.

228
00:10:01,080 --> 00:10:02,879
Yes or no, you need to give a straight answer.

229
00:10:02,879 --> 00:10:04,399
Is she leaving or not?

230
00:10:04,679 --> 00:10:05,519
Then what?

231
00:10:06,960 --> 00:10:08,799
You mean I should go abroad with her,

232
00:10:09,080 --> 00:10:10,320
and then die there?

233
00:10:10,320 --> 00:10:11,200
Leaving her all alone?

234
00:10:11,200 --> 00:10:12,519
If you're asking for my opinion,

235
00:10:12,960 --> 00:10:13,720
if it were me,

236
00:10:13,879 --> 00:10:15,080
I'd make it quick and clean.

237
00:10:15,279 --> 00:10:16,039
Give her an answer.

238
00:10:16,039 --> 00:10:17,240
Don't keep her waiting.

239
00:10:17,240 --> 00:10:17,879
Fine.

240
00:10:18,440 --> 00:10:19,440
I'm taking off, Lao Lu.

241
00:10:19,879 --> 00:10:21,360
I'll thank you on behalf of Staff Officer He.

242
00:10:21,600 --> 00:10:22,279
I'm leaving.

243
00:10:23,519 --> 00:10:24,559
Don't drag this out!

244
00:10:25,159 --> 00:10:25,799
Tomorrow!

245
00:10:25,799 --> 00:10:27,039
Give her an answer tomorrow!

246
00:10:33,879 --> 00:10:34,679
Always worrying.

247
00:10:36,080 --> 00:10:36,759
Fatty.

248
00:10:37,840 --> 00:10:40,480
Is Old Chen's illness really that bad?

249
00:10:59,279 --> 00:10:59,879
Lao Lu.

250
00:11:00,559 --> 00:11:01,159
This way.

251
00:11:06,159 --> 00:11:06,960
Young man, what would you like to buy?

252
00:11:06,960 --> 00:11:07,480
I'll take a newspaper.

253
00:11:07,480 --> 00:11:08,360
A newspaper, huh?

254
00:11:08,480 --> 00:11:09,679
Here, just arrived.

255
00:11:17,360 --> 00:11:18,480
You want this book too?

256
00:11:49,399 --> 00:11:50,080
Hurry, hurry, hurry!

257
00:11:50,919 --> 00:11:51,360
Let's go!

258
00:11:53,960 --> 00:11:54,399
Hurry!

259
00:11:58,480 --> 00:11:59,240
Don't run!

260
00:12:03,080 --> 00:12:03,879
Stop right there!

261
00:12:06,720 --> 00:12:07,399
Don't run!

262
00:12:08,960 --> 00:12:09,679
Don't run!

263
00:12:13,639 --> 00:12:14,320
Stop right there!

264
00:12:17,799 --> 00:12:18,720
I said stop!

265
00:12:20,360 --> 00:12:21,080
Get in the car, quick!

266
00:13:02,799 --> 00:13:04,320
No, we have to go back to the shop.

267
00:13:09,000 --> 00:13:09,799
What happened?

268
00:13:10,879 --> 00:13:11,960
Where are Fatty and Lao Lu?

269
00:13:17,519 --> 00:13:18,519
Bai Lingling's men.

270
00:13:23,879 --> 00:13:25,279
Nothing is missing from the shop.

271
00:13:25,320 --> 00:13:26,799
They came specifically for the genealogy book.

272
00:13:42,039 --> 00:13:42,679
I...

273
00:13:42,960 --> 00:13:43,720
Fatty!

274
00:13:46,399 --> 00:13:47,399
Old Chen!

275
00:13:47,440 --> 00:13:48,279
Don't move, don't move.

276
00:13:48,600 --> 00:13:49,559
Ow, ow, ow!

277
00:13:49,960 --> 00:13:50,919
Are you okay?

278
00:13:51,759 --> 00:13:53,480
This piece of junk, apart from being cold,

279
00:13:53,480 --> 00:13:54,639
has no effect at all.

280
00:13:54,639 --> 00:13:55,759
Rub it for me, rub it, rub it.

281
00:13:56,000 --> 00:13:57,000
So just now,

282
00:13:57,000 --> 00:13:58,840
you saw a group of men in black walking over,

283
00:13:59,080 --> 00:14:00,320
and immediately hid?

284
00:14:00,879 --> 00:14:01,679
Yeah.

285
00:14:01,960 --> 00:14:02,960
I also heard

286
00:14:02,960 --> 00:14:04,679
that what they're looking for is the genealogy book.

287
00:14:07,240 --> 00:14:08,039
Did we lose them?

288
00:14:09,080 --> 00:14:09,919
Lost... lost them.

289
00:14:09,919 --> 00:14:10,639
This way.

290
00:14:14,240 --> 00:14:15,759
The genealogy book should be hidden in this shop.

291
00:14:15,919 --> 00:14:16,559
Search carefully.

292
00:14:16,559 --> 00:14:17,240
Yes, sir.

293
00:14:20,799 --> 00:14:21,600
Let's go, let's go.

294
00:14:21,759 --> 00:14:23,639
Good thing I have the genealogy book on me.

295
00:14:23,960 --> 00:14:25,039
Since they didn't find the genealogy book,

296
00:14:25,039 --> 00:14:26,519
they definitely won't let this go.

297
00:14:26,720 --> 00:14:27,679
I have an idea.

298
00:14:28,039 --> 00:14:29,159
Rather than sitting around waiting to die,

299
00:14:29,159 --> 00:14:30,279
we might as well take the initiative.
